Motor vehicle dealer DT Dobie and NCBA Bank have partnered to offer potential buyers of the VW Polo Vivo an asset finance proposition. The partnership will see customers benefit from up to 95 per cent financing from NCBA and free fuel for one year from DT Dobie. Customers will also enjoy up to 60 months repayment period and, through the bank's bancassurance arm in collaboration with Heritage, will get a 15 per cent cash back on the annual insurance premium, subject to a satisfactory driver behaviour score.